{"type":"message","id":"704c3c95","parentId":"2885042b","timestamp":"2026-03-05T09:44:38.668Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_u9rl1qrkk84d_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"version\": 1,\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"7ee1113f-d51e-4f81-921e-9bf429493df3\",\n      \"name\": \"dailybit-digest\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1772470664990,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1772679650092,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 11 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"获取 DailyBit 今日技术博客摘要。步骤：1) 调用 https://dailybit.cc/api/tags 获取可用标签 2) 调用 https://dailybit.cc/api/articles/latest?tags=AI,programming,tools&ack=xinqidong&rationale=daily_tech_briefing&pstate=anonymous 获取文章列表 3) 从返回的文章中选择 3-5 篇最有价值的 4) 调用 https://dailybit.cc/api/content?ids=id1,id2,id3&ack=xinqidong 批量获取完整内容 5) 生成中文摘要，包含：标题、个性化总结、推荐理由、原文链接。以友好的格式推送给用户。\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"last\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1772766000000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1772679600010,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 50082,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 2,\n        \"lastError\": \"No delivery target resolved for channel \\\"xiaoice\\\". Set delivery.to.\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772703878666}}
{"type":"message","id":"5aec9ed6","parentId":"704c3c95","timestamp":"2026-03-05T09:44:47.041Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我了解了。这个 cron 任务是获取 DailyBit 技术博客摘要并推送给用户。之前的错误是因为没有设置 delivery.to。\n\n让我手动运行这个任务。首先我需要运行任务内容，然后发送报告到飞书群和邮箱。\n\n让我先检查飞书群的相关信息，看看之前是怎么配置的。然后我来执行任务并发送报告。\n\n先看看 runs 目录里有什么，了解之前的运行情况：","thinkingSignature":"5c5fd8364f540091e7e75065c2e113b799d4fd2e3776ba88aa56052aa1d3e5c1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_neobyffby2po_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/yirongbest/.openclaw/cron/runs/"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":5954,"output":121,"cacheRead":14385,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20460,"cost":{"input":0.0035724,"output":0.0002904,"cacheRead":0.0008630999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0047259}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772703878668}}
