{"type":"message","id":"de7087a9","parentId":"248f7af0","timestamp":"2026-03-05T09:50:57.649Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我创建一个联系人文档。","thinkingSignature":"8b1973c6cad3d4ce49a74e78a439c50243633019d5cb4db26b5c073c175b9b9f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gzwokosit2pl_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 联系人通讯录\n\n## 格式说明\n| 姓名 | 邮箱 | 飞书ID | 备注 |\n|------|------|--------|------|\n| 小明 | yuyirong@xiaoice.cn | ou_1a037689464e44e8651500ab98ebf019 | 主人 |\n\n---\n\n## 发送规则\n1. **指定邮箱发送** → 使用 Gmail MCP `send_email`\n2. **飞书私聊** → 使用 `message` channel=feishu, target=飞书ID\n3. **飞书群** → 使用 `message` channel=feishu, target=群ID\n4. **小冰对话** → 需要配置 xiaoice channel 的 delivery.to\n\n---\n\n## 快速查询\n\n### 小明\n- **邮箱**: yuyirong@xiaoice.cn\n- **飞书ID**: ou_1a037689464e44e8651500ab98ebf019\n- **用途**: 主人账号，日报/摘要发送目标\n","file_path":"/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace/memory/contacts.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":38603,"output":274,"cacheRead":14385,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53262,"cost":{"input":0.0231618,"output":0.0006575999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0008630999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0246825}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772704243918}}
