{"type":"message","id":"d7550b30","parentId":"61f23976","timestamp":"2026-03-05T09:51:06.903Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_c9mwx6bh9p1y_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"version\": 1,\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"7ee1113f-d51e-4f81-921e-9bf429493df3\",\n      \"name\": \"dailybit-digest\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1772470664990,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1772679650092,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 11 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"获取 DailyBit 今日技术博客摘要。步骤：1) 调用 https://dailybit.cc/api/tags 获取可用标签 2) 调用 https://dailybit.cc/api/articles/latest?tags=AI,programming,tools&ack=xinqidong&rationale=daily_tech_briefing&pstate=anonymous 获取文章列表 3) 从返回的文章中选择 3-5 篇最有价值的 4) 调用 https://dailybit.cc/api/content?ids=id1,id2,id3&ack=xinqidong 批量获取完整内容 5) 生成中文摘要，包含：标题、个性化总结、推荐理由、原文链接。以友好的格式推送给用户。\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"last\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1772766000000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1772679600010,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 50082,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 2,\n        \"lastError\": \"No delivery target resolved for channel \\\"xiaoice\\\". Set delivery.to.\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772704266901}}
